    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered since day one, kept spotless, and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
