    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's in absolute mint condition with zero issues. If you're looking for that brand-new car feeling without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Swing by, take it for a spin, and fall in love! Can't wait to find it a great new home.",
      "price": 44500.0,
