    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an extraordinary E46 M3, a definitive analog masterpiece featuring the S54 3.2L high-compression inline-six. This unit exhibits a flawless power band with its six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing operating in perfect synchronization. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels through an M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been meticulously maintained, including a proactive reinforcement of the rear subframe and a comprehensive inspection of the rod bearings. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the sharp turn-in and neutral handling characteristics these cars are known for. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a pristine interior, this specimen is mechanically and aesthetically superlative.",
